              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The neutron  spectrum  was  corrected  for   detector",
                " efficiency."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Comparison with  cross-sections  published  by   R.L.",
                " Bramblett,  et al.,  H.Beil,  et al., R.R.Harvey, et",
                " al.  (for Pb),  and by P.H.Cannington,  et al.  (for",
                " Pr),  which  indicate  the  structure  of  the giant",
                " dipole resonance for these nuclei,  shows  agreement",
                " between  the  energies  of  the  peaks  found in the",
                " present work and the energies En  =  E-B,  where  En",
                " corresponds to a peak in the cross-section curve,  B",
                " is the threshold for producing a given state in  the",
                " daughter nucleus. Only ground state transitions (for",
                " Pr) or ground state and the first two excited  state",
                " transitions (for Pb) should be invoked."
              ]
            }
          ],
